item.title:
@KordingLab I'm sorry, but the linguistic games they play in this cell culture stuff bugs me a bit... 

They are defining "prediction" using MI between a binary stim signal and the time-shifted spiking activity. 

That doesn't tell you whether the system is making a prediction.

